by sstok at 2014-08-17T07:13:46Z

You can actually solve this by overwriting the getExtension method.
Which is recommended by @matthiasnoback http://php-and-symfony.matthiasnoback.nl/2013/10/symfony2-some-things-i-dont-like-about-bundles/

Removing this validation can have unexpected consequence.

Edit. Missed the original conversation https://github.com/symfony/symfony/commit/97f66e93ac78a2f775c67ff38bb362b1e65da1d8#commitcomment-7399987

